      "resumen": "Architecture patterns for deploying robust and scalable LangGraph agents.",
      "contenido": [
        "## From Demo to Production",
        "",
        "LangGraph agents are powerful, but going from a notebook to production requires considering: state, errors, observability, and scalability.",
        "",
        "## Recommended Architecture",
        "",
        "```",
        "┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐",
        "│   FastAPI   │────▶│  LangGraph  │────▶│   Tools     │",
        "│   Gateway   │     │   Engine    │     │  (Sandboxed)│",
        "└─────────────┘     └─────────────┘     └─────────────┘",
        "       │                   │                   │",
        "       ▼                   ▼                   ▼",
        "┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐",
        "│   Redis     │     │ PostgreSQL  │     │  Monitoring │",
        "│   (Cache)   │     │ (Checkpts)  │     │  (Grafana)  │",
        "└─────────────┘     └─────────────┘     └─────────────┘",
        "```",
        "",
        "## Checkpointing for Resilience",
        "",
        "```python",
        "from langgraph.checkpoint.postgres import PostgresSaver",
        "",
        "checkpointer = PostgresSaver.from_conn_string(",
        "    os.environ['DATABASE_URL']",
        ")",
        "",
        "graph = workflow.compile(checkpointer=checkpointer)",
        "```",
        "",
        "## Error Handling",
        "",
        "```python",
        "@node",
        "def tool_executor(state: State) -> State:",
        "    try:",
        "        result = execute_tool(state.tool_call)",
        "    except ToolTimeoutError:",
        "        return state.with_error('Tool timeout')",
        "    except RateLimitError:",
        "        # Retry with backoff",
        "        raise NodeRetry(delay=60)",
        "```",
        "",
        "## Observability",
        "",
        "- **LangSmith**: Complete traces for each execution",
        "- **OpenTelemetry**: Custom metrics and spans",
        "- **Prometheus**: Token counters, latency, errors",
        "",
        "## Rate Limiting",
        "",
        "```python",
        "from slowapi import Limiter",
        "",
        "limiter = Limiter(key_func=get_user_id)",
        "",
        "@app.post('/agent/invoke')",
        "@limiter.limit('10/minute')",
        "async def invoke_agent(request: AgentRequest):",
        "    ...",
        "```",
        "",
        "## Conclusion",
        "",
        "Production agents need to be treated as distributed systems: with persistent state, failure handling, and complete observability."
      ]
